text: Sib and Suran castle is a castle in Sib and Suran County, and is one of the attractions of Sib and Suran County. This castle was built by the Barakzehi dynasty. == Sources == Category:Castles in Iran Category:Qajar castles Category:Buildings and structures in Sistan and Baluchestan Province Category:National Works of Iran Category:Qajar dynasty
title: Sib and Suran castle
